The moment I heard about bacon jam, I knew I had to make it. This recipe combines the tantalizing flavor of bacon with onion jam. Spread this remarkable confection on a tomato sandwich. Fill acorn squash with bacon jam and chunks of tart apple. Or make, quite simply, the naughtiest creation ever: bacon rugelach with salted peanuts. The moment I heard about bacon jam, I knew I had to make it. This recipe combines the tantalizing flavor of bacon with onion jam. Spread this remarkable confection on a tomato sandwich. Fill acorn squash with bacon jam and chunks of tart apple. Or make, quite simply, the naughtiest creation ever: bacon rugelach with salted peanuts.